ices out there\n    - BCC Please\n    - Thanks, No\n    - Sentenc.es\n    - Etc.\n- Describe own ideas\n    - allcaps.com\n    - subjectline.com\n- Ask for others ideas','Netiquette',0,'','inherit','open','open','','271-revision','','','2008-08-05 17:18:24','2008-08-05 21:18:24','',271,'http://burningones.com/2008/08/05/271-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(273,2,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Thesis: Tagging with an everything-you-can-possibly-think-might-apply-to-this-item approach is counterproductive and exhausting.  Instead, think of the context you\'re in and create tags based on what you believe you may be interested in some time from now.\r\n\r\n- Introduction\r\n- Currently used tagging systems\r\n- Strategy #1: Everything-You-Can-Possibly-Think-Might-Apply-To-This-Item\r\n- Strategy #2: Think-Before-You-Even-Start-And-Stay-Within-Your-Boundaries\r\n- Conclusion','Tag-Based Anything: The Strategy That Might Actually Be Helpful.',0,'Lessons learned about how to properly utilize tagging from my initial forays into tagging (Delicious, Cha-Ching, Firefox, iTunes, etc.) till now.','draft','open','open','','','','','2008-08-07 11:30:01','2008-08-07 15:30:01','',0,'http://burningones.com/?p=273',0,'post','',0),(274,2,'2008-08-07 11:29:43','2008-08-07 15:29:43','Thesis: Tagging with an everything-you-can-possibly-think-might-apply-to-this-item approach is counterproductive and exhausting.  Instead, think of the context you\'re in and create tags based on what you believe you may be interested in some time from now.\n\n- Introduction\n- Currently used tagging systems\n- Strategy #1: Everything-You-Can-Possibly-Think-Might-Apply-To-This-Item\n- Strategy #2: Think-Before-You-Even-Start-And-Stay-Within-Your-Boundaries\n- Conclusion','Tag-Based Anything: The Strategy That Might Actually Be Helpful.',0,'Lessons learned about how to properly utilize tagging from my initial forays into tagging (Delicious, Cha-Ching, Firefox, iTunes, etc.) till now.','inherit','o